headline: Keysight Enables 6G Digital Twin Research at the University of Texas at Austin
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., October 07, 2025--Keysight said 6G@UT at the University of Texas at Austin chose Keysight’s 6G solutions for research on digital twins.
